      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEARTBREAK HONEY (4) was prominent throughout when winning two back then got further back last time but came home hard into third and beaten 8 lengths at this track (30.50). Makes plenty of appeal. SILKEN OWL (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (35.15) in a Mix 6/7 at Sandown. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Key runner on best form. QUEEN GODDESS (2) had the drop on the lead from the inside before drawing clear to score (30.13) at this track in a Novice race over 520m. Form from her last run is proving strong. Deserves serious consideration again. HOT MINUTE (3) jumped best and was never headed last time. Right in the mix again.",
